        "subject": "LU-15367 tests: Combined patches",
        "message": "LU-15367 tests: Combined patches\n\nThis is a very strange trick I'm doing - there are two\nseparate patch series which are both needed to implement\nand test iotrace-to-multiop conversion.\n\nI don't want to combine the series and I don't want to wait\nfor both of them to land, so this is a special temporary\npatch combining all of those patches.\n\nThis combines basically all of the patches for LU-15367.\n\nTest-Parameters: forbuildonly\nTest-Parameters: neverlandthis\nSigned-off-by: Patrick Farrell <pfarrell@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I5ecc50ec118ee84c9436df8c041fd1cb5c1c4ba0\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
